cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.CG, cs.LG

The paper deals with 3D reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of plane priors is also relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and computational geometry (cs.CG). Finally, the paper presents a novel algorithm, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) as well.
